name: [Tier1] Loot Chest!
description:
Welcome to the Loot Chest project!

We have currently just set up 3 Loot Chests for the community to join in varying tiers!
Each Loot Chest collection has different prizes that may be looted!

This Loot Chest consists of 1000 prizes!
1 winner will receive 200tezos!
250 winners will receive 10tezos!
749 winners will receive 1tezos!

And sadly, the remaining loot chests will be empty :(

All you have to do to enter is buy one of these loot chests and wait for your possible prizes when the collection is completed!
Good luck everyone and be sure to check out the two other Loot Chests as well!
Twitter, telegram, and discord will be made public in the next week where we will giveaway some more loot chests!
We are super excited and can't wait to see who has the luck to loot a huge chest!
